messageBody:
> It is *not* a primary purpose of DBC to verify the correctness of
> implementation.

Purposes can change. The purpose of the Internet was first to serve
the army. Then it had a academic purpose. And now it has no special
purpose.

I bought your book today so I hope you will not be too angry with
me...
